milestones.description: Bevan Congdon has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking Vic Pollard's record
Dayle Hadlee has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs, going past Bishan Bedi's 1
Bevan Congdon has become the top scorer for NZ in ODIs with 237 runs, going past Ken Wadsworth's 144
Dayle Hadlee has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for NZ, going past Peter Coman's 1
Bevan Congdon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for NZ, going past Hastings
Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs, going past Doug Walters's 5
Bevan Congdon and Hastings's 84-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 49 between Bevan Congdon and Hastings
Howarth and Hadlee's 17-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Howarth and Hadlee
